{
  "title": "Linux中的15个基本‘ls’命令示例",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<embed id=\"xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd\" type=\"application/thunder_download_plugin\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em;\">ls命令是Linux系统中最被频繁使用的命令之一，我相信ls命令一定是你进入一台Linux系统的电脑打开命令提示符后第一个使用的命令。我们每天都在频繁地使用ls命令,即使我们可能没有意识也从来用不到所有可用的选项。本文中，我们将讨论下一些基本的ls命令并且覆盖尽可能多的有关参数来讲解。</span><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">1. 不带任何选项列出文件</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">不带选项的ls命令来光秃秃地列出文件和目录，我们是不能看到像文件类型、大小、修改日期和时间、权限以及链接这样具体的信息的。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls\n0001.pcap        Desktop    Downloads         index.html   install.log.syslog  Pictures  Templates\nanaconda-ks.cfg  Documents  fbcmd_update.php  install.log  Music               Public    Videos</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">2 带 –l 选项列出文件列表</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">你看，ls -l（-l是字母不是“1”）就能展示出是文件还是目录，它的大小、修改日期和时间、文件或目录的名字以及文件的属主和它的权限。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -l\ntotal 176\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root   683 Aug 19 09:59 0001.pcap\n-rw-------. 1 root root  1586 Jul 31 02:17 anaconda-ks.cfg\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Desktop\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Documents\ndrwxr-xr-x. 4 root root  4096 Aug 16 02:55 Downloads\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 21262 Aug 12 12:42 fbcmd_update.php\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 46701 Jul 31 09:58 index.html\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 48867 Jul 31 02:17 install.log\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 11439 Jul 31 02:13 install.log.syslog\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Music\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Pictures\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Public\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Templates\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Videos</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">3. 浏览隐藏文件</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">列出所有文件包括以‘.’开头的隐藏文件。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -a\n.                .bashrc  Documents         .gconfd          install.log         .nautilus     .pulse-cookie\n..               .cache   Downloads         .gnome2          install.log.syslog  .netstat.swp  .recently-used.xbel\n0001.pcap        .config  .elinks           .gnome2_private  .kde                .opera        .spice-vdagent\nanaconda-ks.cfg  .cshrc   .esd_auth         .gtk-bookmarks   .libreoffice        Pictures      .tcshrc\n.bash_history    .dbus    .fbcmd            .gvfs            .local              .pki          Templates\n.bash_logout     Desktop  fbcmd_update.php  .ICEauthority    .mozilla            Public        Videos\n.bash_profile    .digrc   .gconf            index.html       Music               .pulse        .wireshark</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">4. 用 -lh 选项来以易读方式列出文件</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">用-lh组合选项，以易读方式来显示大小。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -lh\ntotal 176K\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root  683 Aug 19 09:59 0001.pcap\n-rw-------. 1 root root 1.6K Jul 31 02:17 anaconda-ks.cfg\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root 4.0K Jul 31 02:48 Desktop\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root 4.0K Jul 31 02:48 Documents\ndrwxr-xr-x. 4 root root 4.0K Aug 16 02:55 Downloads\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root  21K Aug 12 12:42 fbcmd_update.php\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root  46K Jul 31 09:58 index.html\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root  48K Jul 31 02:17 install.log\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root  12K Jul 31 02:13 install.log.syslog\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root 4.0K Jul 31 02:48 Music\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root 4.0K Jul 31 02:48 Pictures\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root 4.0K Jul 31 02:48 Public\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root 4.0K Jul 31 02:48 Templates\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root 4.0K Jul 31 02:48 Videos</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">5. 以尾部以‘/’字符结尾的方式列出文件和目录</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">使用 ls 命令的 -F 选项，会在每个目录的末尾添加“/”字符显示。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -F\n0001.pcap        Desktop/    Downloads/        index.html   install.log.syslog  Pictures/  Templates/\nanaconda-ks.cfg  Documents/  fbcmd_update.php  install.log  Music/              Public/    Videos/</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">6. 倒序列出文件</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">ls -r 选项能以倒序方式显示文件和目录。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -r\nVideos     Public    Music               install.log  fbcmd_update.php  Documents  anaconda-ks.cfg\nTemplates  Pictures  install.log.syslog  index.html   Downloads         Desktop    0001.pcap</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">7. 递归列出子目录</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">ls -R 选项能列出非常长的目录树，来看看示例输出：</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -R\ntotal 1384\n-rw-------. 1 root     root      33408 Aug  8 17:25 anaconda.log\n-rw-------. 1 root     root      30508 Aug  8 17:25 anaconda.program.log\n./httpd:\ntotal 132\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root     0 Aug 19 03:14 access_log\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 61916 Aug 10 17:55 access_log-20120812\n./lighttpd:\ntotal 68\n-rw-r--r--  1 lighttpd lighttpd  7858 Aug 21 15:26 access.log\n-rw-r--r--. 1 lighttpd lighttpd 37531 Aug 17 18:21 access.log-20120819\n./nginx:\ntotal 12\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root    0 Aug 12 03:17 access.log\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root  390 Aug 12 03:17 access.log-20120812.gz</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">8. 以修改时间倒序列出</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">带-ltr组合选项能以文件或目录的最新修改时间的次序来显示它们。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -ltr\ntotal 176\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 11439 Jul 31 02:13 install.log.syslog\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 48867 Jul 31 02:17 install.log\n-rw-------. 1 root root  1586 Jul 31 02:17 anaconda-ks.cfg\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Desktop\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Videos\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Templates\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Public\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Pictures\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Music\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Documents\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 46701 Jul 31 09:58 index.html\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 21262 Aug 12 12:42 fbcmd_update.php\ndrwxr-xr-x. 4 root root  4096 Aug 16 02:55 Downloads\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root   683 Aug 19 09:59 0001.pcap</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">9. 按文件大小排序</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">带-lS组合选项能按文件从大到小的次序显示。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -lS\ntotal 176\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 48867 Jul 31 02:17 install.log\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 46701 Jul 31 09:58 index.html\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 21262 Aug 12 12:42 fbcmd_update.php\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 11439 Jul 31 02:13 install.log.syslog\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Desktop\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Documents\ndrwxr-xr-x. 4 root root  4096 Aug 16 02:55 Downloads\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Music\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Pictures\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Public\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Templates\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root  4096 Jul 31 02:48 Videos\n-rw-------. 1 root root  1586 Jul 31 02:17 anaconda-ks.cfg\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root   683 Aug 19 09:59 0001.pcap</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">10. 显示文件或目录的索引节点号</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">我们有时候可以看到一些数字打印在文件或目录名之前，带-i选项就能列出文件或目录的索引节点号。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -i\n20112 0001.pcap        23610 Documents         23793 index.html          23611 Music     23597 Templates\n23564 anaconda-ks.cfg  23595 Downloads            22 install.log         23612 Pictures  23613 Videos\n23594 Desktop          23585 fbcmd_update.php     35 install.log.syslog  23601 Public</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">11. 显示ls命令的版本</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">查看ls命令的版本。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls --version\nls (GNU coreutils) 8.4\nCopyright (C) 2010 Free Software Foundation, Inc.\nLicense GPLv3+: GNU GPL version 3 or later &lt;<a href=\"http://gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">http://gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html</a>&gt;.\nThis is free software: you are free to change and redistribute it.\nThere is NO WARRANTY, to the extent permitted by law.\nWritten by Richard M. Stallman and David MacKenzie.</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">12. 显示帮助页面</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">列出ls命令的选项帮助页面。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls --help\nUsage: ls [OPTION]... [FILE]...</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">13. 列出目录信息</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">用ls -l命令列出/tmp目录下的文件，其中-ld参数可以只显示/tmp目录的信息。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -l /tmp\ntotal 408\ndrwx------. 2 narad narad   4096 Aug  2 02:00 CRX_75DAF8CB7768\n-r--------. 1 root  root  384683 Aug  4 12:28 htop-1.0.1.tar.gz\ndrwx------. 2 root  root    4096 Aug  4 11:20 keyring-6Mfjnk\ndrwx------. 2 root  root    4096 Aug 16 01:33 keyring-pioZJr\ndrwx------. 2 gdm   gdm     4096 Aug 21 11:26 orbit-gdm\ndrwx------. 2 root  root    4096 Aug 19 08:41 pulse-gl6o4ZdxQVrX\ndrwx------. 2 narad narad   4096 Aug  4 08:16 pulse-UDH76ExwUVoU\ndrwx------. 2 gdm   gdm     4096 Aug 21 11:26 pulse-wJtcweUCtvhn\n-rw-------. 1 root  root     300 Aug 16 03:34 yum_save_tx-2012-08-16-03-34LJTAa1.yumtx</pre><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -ld /tmp/\ndrwxrwxrwt. 13 root root 4096 Aug 21 12:48 /tmp/</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">14. 显示文件的UID和GID</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">用ls -n命令来显示文件和目录的UID（译者注：userid，用户ID）和GID（译者注：groupid，组ID）。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># ls -n\ntotal 36\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 500 500 4096 Aug  2 01:52 Downloads\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 500 500 4096 Aug  2 01:52 Music\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 500 500 4096 Aug  2 01:52 Pictures\n-rw-rw-r--. 1 500 500   12 Aug 21 13:06 tmp.txt\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 500 500 4096 Aug  2 01:52 Videos</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">15. ls命令和它的别名</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">我们给ls命令设置如下别名之后，当我们执行ls命令的时候它会默认执行-l选项并且像上文提到的那样显示长列表。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># alias ls=\"ls -l\"</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">注意：我们可以通过不加任何参数的alias命令来看到目前系统中可用的所有alias设置，当然它们同时也可以unalias来取消。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># alias\nalias cp='cp -i'\nalias l.='ls -d .* --color=auto'\nalias ll='ls -l --color=auto'\nalias ls='ls --color=auto'\nalias mv='mv -i'\nalias rm='rm -i'\nalias which='alias | /usr/bin/which --tty-only --read-alias --show-dot --show-tilde'</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; line-height: 24px;\">删除一项之前定义的alias设置，只需用unalias命令即可。</p><pre class=\"language-shell\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392); font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; padding: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, 'Andale Mono', monospace; -webkit-hyphens: none; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; direction: ltr; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240);\"># unalias ls</pre>"
    }
  ]
}